07:26.110 --> 07:27.676
No, he'll think
I'm spying.

07:27.678 --> 07:30.747
No, then just, uh, film
him on your phone then.

07:30.749 --> 07:32.615
Hmm?

07:32.617 --> 07:33.617
Are you serious?

07:33.619 --> 07:34.750
Yes, Ivy.

07:34.752 --> 07:35.851
Now.

07:37.154 --> 07:39.288
- Yeah?
- I want hot chocolate.

07:46.098 --> 07:48.298
Go, go, go!

07:49.535 --> 07:50.834
What are you doing?

07:50.836 --> 07:53.637
