triggers for you here.

10:30.861 --> 10:32.061
That was months ago.

10:32.063 --> 10:33.930
And, and, and
your sponsor said...

10:33.932 --> 10:36.733
Please, let... let Ben
tell me, please.

10:36.735 --> 10:37.733
Please, honey.

10:37.735 --> 10:40.002
OK, I know...

10:40.004 --> 10:42.204
I know I really fucked up
last Christmas.

10:42.206 --> 10:44.210
And the one before that.

10:46.344 --> 10:47.844
It's true.

10:47.846 --> 10:51.116
Yeah, I know I've made
a lot of mistakes.

10:51.850 --> 10:54.084
But...

10:54.086 --> 10:55.819
Now, since I'm doing so good,

10:55.821 --> 10:59.455
and... and with all the support
I'm getting and...

10:59.457 --> 11:02.358
w-with my sponsor?

11:02.360 --> 11:05.261
I honestly didn't
think I'd ever...

11:05.263 --> 11:06.699
feel this good again.

11:11.903 --> 11:13.368
What? You don't believe me?

11:13.370 --> 11:14.469
Sweetie, we do.

11:14.471 --> 11:17.239
Which is why she hid all
the meds and the jewelry.

11:17.241 --> 11:19.844
I was just removing
the temptation.

11:21.913 --> 11:24.917
Wow. Fuck. You're all
still scared of me.

11:26.884 --> 11:30.423
Which is the last thing
I wanna make any of you feel.

11:33.958 --> 11:36.861
You should just... you
should take me back.

11:43.501 --> 11:45.103
Mom, take me back.

11:48.240 --> 11:50.205
<i>Front door.</i>

11:52.110 --> 11:54.911
- Mom?
- You should have known better.

11:54.913 --> 11:56.246
Don't blame him.

11:56.248 --> 11:58.147
It's my fault.

11:58.149 --> 12:00.983
