going to do this again.

12:58.210 --> 12:59.912
Remember?

13:01.413 --> 13:03.414
I remember.

13:09.421 --> 13:10.923
Holly?

13:11.856 --> 13:12.988
Here's the list.

13:12.990 --> 13:14.324
I don't care
who gets what.

13:14.326 --> 13:15.224
Just get it done.

13:15.226 --> 13:16.995
Yeah.

13:29.206 --> 13:31.143
God, damn it!

13:32.076 --> 13:34.145
God, damn it!

13:35.480 --> 13:37.015
We're all set.

13:48.225 --> 13:49.258
It's okay, Mom.

13:49.260 --> 13:50.962
It's for the best.

13:53.631 --> 13:55.300
Seat belt, please.

14:07.946 --> 14:09.378
Mom.

14:09.380 --> 14:11.046
Mom!

14:18.023 --> 14:19.291
What?

14:21.025 --> 14:23.225
I'm thinking.

14:35.005 --> 14:37.175
All right. Come on.

14:48.285 --> 14:49.618
OK.

14:49.620 --> 14:52.722
Here's the deal, and
it is not negotiable.

14:52.724 --> 14:54.293
You get a day.

14:55.125 --> 14:56.693
Are you sure?

14:56.695 --> 14:59.127
So long as you pass the drug
test I'm about to administer.

14:59.129 --> 15:00.629
Stay clean while you're here,

15:00.631 --> 15:03.098
and that this time tomorrow
you are back in Sober Living.

15:03.100 --> 15:04.267
Yeah, OK.

15:04.269 --> 15:05.535
Now, I'm not done.

15:05.537 --> 15:06.603
These are our terms,

15:06.605 --> 15:09.171
and I don't give a shit
if you hate these rules.

15:09.173 --> 15:11.574
You do not leave
my sight ever.

15:11.576 --> 15:14.042
You do not close
the door to your room,

15:14.044 --> 15:16.212
where, by the way, I will
be sleeping on the floor,

15:16.214 --> 15:17.446
and if you try
to sneak off,

15:17.448 --> 15:19.181
if your bed so much
as make squeak,

15:19.183 --> 15:21.084
I will be all over you

15:21.086 --> 15:25.356
because, for the next 24 hours,
you are mine. All mine. Got it?

15:26.157 --> 15:27.459
I got it.

15:28.460 --> 15:29.392
Good.

15:29.394 --> 15:31.096
Let's get you tested.

15:38.470 --> 15:40.069
Mom.

15:40.071 --> 15:42.504
Relax, I'm not going to be
looking at your privates.

15:42.506 --> 15:43.339
OK, then.

15:43.341 --> 15:45.273
I will be keeping
my eyes on you.

15:45.275 --> 15:47.078
Just like I said.

15:51.249 --> 15:52.448
This is so not cool.

15:52.450 --> 15:55.086
Nothing about this
is cool, Ben.

15:59.157 --> 16:00.189
Come on, pee-pee time.

16:00.191 --> 16:01.757
Shut up.

16:03.461 --> 16:05.494
Do you want me to
turn the faucet on?

16:05.496 --> 16:06.631
Stop.

16:09.500 --> 16:11.633
- Shh.
- All right, all right, all right.

16:11.635 --> 16:14.203
- Sometimes it helps.
- Mm-hmm.

16:14.205 --> 16:15.671
- What are you doing?
- OK.

16:15.673 --> 16:19.175
- There's a surprise coming.
- What surprise?

16:19.177 --> 16:20.343
Do you trust me?

16:20.345 --> 16:21.344
- Yes!
- Yes, I do.

16:21.346 --> 16:22.811
Awesome. That's awesome.

16:22.813 --> 16:24.546
Good. Good to hear.

16:24.548 --> 16:25.415
All right.

16:25.417 --> 16:27.282
- You close your eyes.
- Yeah.

16:27.284 --> 16:29.151
- Can you see anything?
- No.

16:29.153 --> 16:30.489
OK, no peaking.

16:33.357 --> 16:35.257
I hear something.

16:35.259 --> 16:37.660
- When I was your age, this was my favorite.
- It's gross.

16:37.662 --> 16:39.695
Ivy, chill out.

16:39.697 --> 16:42.065
Liam doesn't like crust.

16:42.067 --> 16:44.269
There's a crust-less option

16:44.802 --> 16:46.201
in the works.

16:46.203 --> 16:47.538
Oh, really?

16:49.274 --> 16:50.640
Are you two ready?

16:50.642 --> 16:51.840
Yes.

16:51.842 --> 16:53.508
<i>Back door.</i>

16:53.510 --> 16:56.481
OK, open your eyes and feast.

17:00.418 --> 17:02.350
- Yum!
- Right?

17:02.352 --> 17:04.152
