17:04.154 --> 17:05.421
What have you done?

17:05.423 --> 17:07.222
I know. I know.
There's no going back.

17:07.223 --> 17:11.393
Mm-hmm. More, please!

17:11.395 --> 17:13.662
But Ashley's
wings have glitter.

17:13.664 --> 17:17.232
Well, we are going to bedazzle
these things like crazy.

17:17.233 --> 17:18.834
Mom, seriously,
they're so good.

17:18.836 --> 17:20.236
I don't want to brag.

17:20.238 --> 17:22.270
Well, yeah, I do.
These are gonna be good.

17:26.711 --> 17:28.212
Ben?

17:40.290 --> 17:42.859
Boy. Hey, buddy.

17:47.231 --> 17:48.230
Hi Mama.

17:48.232 --> 17:50.298
You knew it.

17:50.300 --> 17:52.301
You came back for Ponce.

17:52.303 --> 17:54.202
Busted.

17:54.204 --> 17:55.473
Actually, no.

18:05.849 --> 18:07.752
OK, let's party.

18:12.390 --> 18:13.555
You know, I really
wouldn't appreciate it if you leave me.

18:13.557 --> 18:14.757
