It hurts to think about
the shit I've done.

18:33.912 --> 18:35.911
And what I'm learning in
recovery is I can't undo

18:35.913 --> 18:38.847
what I've done, but I can
do it differently now.

18:38.849 --> 18:40.182
I think we're good here.

18:40.184 --> 18:41.449
One... just one sec, Ivy.

18:41.451 --> 18:43.518
What I mean is, is
